  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img data-imgfileid=\"501968436\" data-type=\"png\" width=\"1800\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-w=\"1080\" data-ratio=\"0.42592592592592593\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=40fa7a62&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2Fg0kpxARkI2TVonTE2u6v73eSQx09tW492hYQQFSWicadRia8OFDjicbZ33VzwFdjacbSzgfD7D4tmew0wSULI0yAg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <blockquote style=\"padding:16px 20px;color:rgb(80, 80, 80);visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:18px;border-color:initial;line-height:1.64;box-sizing:border-box !important;quotes:none;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;border-radius:4px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;margin-top:20px;border-width:initial;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:20px;border-style:none;\">\n   <p style=\"max-width: 100%;outline: 0px;border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;visibility: visible;text-align: left;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;visibility: visible;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">「有意思小周刊」是我利用零碎时间，梳理记录一周的日常阅读与思考内容。目的是为以后更好构建自己知识体系，也为了将这些内容分享给你。</span></span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <h3 style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;white-space: normal;line-height: 2em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(1, 194, 96);\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">以下是这期值得关注的内容</span></strong></span></h3>\n  <h3 style=\"margin: 24px 8px 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;text-align: left;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">📰 推荐阅读</span></span></h3>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;line-height: 1.6em;text-indent: 0em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;\">1. AI 辅助前端动画开发</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;line-height: 1.6em;text-indent: 0em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;\">2. UI 走查这件事，90% 问题都写在 DevTools 里</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;line-height: 1.6em;text-indent: 0em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;\">3. AI 驱动工作流 - 自动化项目分析与线上问题修复</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;line-height: 1.6em;text-indent: 0em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;\">4. 如何设计大规模 AI 系统（上）</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;line-height: 1.6em;text-indent: 0em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;\">5. 出海技术挑战——Lalamove智能告警降噪</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;line-height: 1.6em;text-indent: 0em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;\">6. 大模型原理（英文）</span></p>\n  <h4 style=\"margin: 24px 8px 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;text-align: left;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">🛠️&nbsp;</span><strong><span leaf=\"\">资源·工具</span></strong></span></h4>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-indent: 0em;text-wrap: wrap;text-align: left;line-height: 1.6em;\"><ne-clipboard data=\"%7B%22type%22%3A%22fragment%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22%23fragment%22%2C%22children%22%3A%5B%7B%22type%22%3A%22element%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u878ddb87%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22oli%22%2C%22attrs%22%3A%7B%22list%22%3A%22u4ae5d82c%22%2C%22indexType%22%3A0%2C%22indexStyle%22%3A%7B%7D%2C%22fid%22%3A%22u28f86a53%22%2C%22pa