px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;\">3. Screentell：提供一个简单直观的浏览器端屏幕录制与编辑工具</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 8px 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;text-align: left;line-height: 1.6em;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">📚 近期书单</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;line-height: 1.6em;text-indent: 0em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-right: 8px; margin-left: 8px; line-height: 1.6em; text-indent: 0em; margin-bottom: 0px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">1.&nbsp;</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;\">《真希望我父母读过这本书》</span></p>\n  <p data-track=\"34\" style=\"visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:18px;border-color:initial;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;outline:0px;max-width:100%;margin-top:20px;border-width:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0em;border-style:initial;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-cropselx1=\"0\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely1=\"0\" data-cropsely2=\"65\" data-ratio=\"0.11296296296296296\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width:578px;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:center;height:auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=be35e013&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fg0kpxARkI2QPgPA868wyn0LFMFlv18uosEWwB4iaKPdBBHJlD4GYRHOytPia6moa4MPQDibjKXtvUvts27RcWa5OQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></span></p>\n  <ne-clipboard source=\"https%3A%2F%2Fwww.yuque.com%2Fqone%2Fyys%2Fmgggk18me5v4b2gu%2Fedit%3Ftoc_node_uuid%3DVMfwSFI9ToVb8SjE%23YHgv6\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"></ne-clipboard>\n  <h2 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:24px 8px 8px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;text-align:left;\"><span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(1, 194, 96);font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px;\">▌AI 辅助前端动画开发</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">链接：</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link mp_article_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzAxNDEwNjk5OQ==&amp;mid=2650542238&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=cd1abf99bd651f4e7c891d9d4c9905f8&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"></a><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/ag2W9-rpQEyQB9RmDkywCQ\" target=\"_blank\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/ag2W9-rpQEyQB9RmDkywCQ</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">本文介绍了AI辅助前端动画开发的实践方案与技术思路，核心围绕解决传统动画开发中“参数难获取、沟通成本高、反复返工”等痛点展开。作者以 After Effects（AE）为动效源头，构建了一套基于 MCP（Model Context Protocol）工具链 + Cursor AI IDE 的协作工作流，强调“L3级自动驾驶”——即AI生成关键步骤，但保留开发者随时介入、校验与调整的灵活性。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><img data-imgfileid=\"501968438\" data-type=\"other\" width=\"1080\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-w=\"1080\" data-ratio=\"0.25\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=fa988e78&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Fg0kpxARkI2TVonTE2u6v73eSQx09tW49KIyiaz5GMRsRJWSmnaA2VaCS7HoWuFgH9ph25D4yeOLJKibDnTm9dKbA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <h2 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:24px 8px 8px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;text-align:left;\"><span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(1, 194, 96);font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px;\">▌UI 走查这件事，90% 问题都写在 DevTools 里</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">链接：</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link mp_article_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzAwNTc0NDExMA==&amp;mid=2650307690&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=22c85f7e07dbd9f841b62193b5a7632e&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"></a><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/GtW-lw1VBw0d0gVnGOYeUw\" target=\"_blank\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/GtW-lw1VBw0d0gVnGOYeUw</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">DevTools（开发者工具）被设计为设计师与工程师共同的尺子，通过可视化和实时修改样式、布局与计算值，帮助快速、精准地进行 UI 走查，尤其在间距问题上效果显著。文章从设计师视角介绍了如何使用 DevTools 的核心面板与技巧，并强调在移动端走查、以及 AI 辅助走查的现状与未来发展。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><img data-imgfileid=\"501968439\" data-type=\"other\" width=\"1080\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-w=\"1080\" data-ratio=\"0.6574074074074074\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ba3fda16&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Fg0kpxARkI2TVonTE2u6v73eSQx09tW49P7eHKiczCokibTqskQzLADFrjzAdIrGSlynI9ZVfImTLiarxza89woa5A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <h2 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:24px 8px 8px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;text-align:left;\"><span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(1, 194, 96);font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px;\">▌AI 驱动工作流 - 自动化项目分析与线上问题修复</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">链接：</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://tech.qimao.com/ai-qu-dong-gong-zuo-liu-zi-dong-hua-xiang-mu-fen-xi-yu-xian-shang-wen-ti-xiu-fu/\" target=\"_blank\">https://tech.qimao.com/ai-qu-dong-gong-zuo-liu-zi-dong-hua-xiang-mu-fen-xi-yu-xian-shang-wen-ti-xiu-fu/</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">本文提出一个 AI 驱动的可持续维护系统，通过自动化线上问题修复与自动化线上性能分析，实现从问题出现到修复方案生成的高自动化闭环，目标在于降低人工干预、缩短修复时间并提升可追溯性与可视化。系统以 Sentry 和 Prometheus/Grafana 监控为触发源，结合 Claude Code 等 AI 工具在云端执行分析与修复，最终通过飞书通知与人工确认实现安全落地。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><img data-imgfileid=\"501968440\" data-type=\"png\" width=\"1004\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-w=\"1004\" data-ratio=\"0.9830677290836654\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d8d22137&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2Fg0kpxARkI2TVonTE2u6v73eSQx09tW49QQ6z9vAaicb1O11Ts5lwictBwoawQGnv787E5oK3SOFhfK6ZwdN5xQ1g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <h2 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:24px 8px 8px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;text-align:left;\"><span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(1, 194, 96);font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px;\">▌如何设计大规模 AI 系统（上）</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">链接：</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link mp_article_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzk0ODE3NTMzNg==&amp;mid=2247527522&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=bf48c6fcf5cb33028cd98c64e5a7ce66&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"></a><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/lI1BC6LnrhmIjgASlsRTYQ\" target=\"_blank\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/lI1BC6LnrhmIjgASlsRTYQ</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">本文系统性地阐述了设计和部署大规模 AI 系统的关键阶段与要点，涵盖硬件与基础设施、高级模型训练与推理技术、以及性能分析与优化等方面，强调从开发到运营各环节的协同、成本与能耗的权衡，以及在大规模场景中提升训练、推理效率与系统可扩展性的实用方法。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><img data-imgfileid=\"501968441\" data-type=\"other\" width=\"1080\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-w=\"1080\" data-ratio=\"0.2824074074074074\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7dc48401&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Fg0kpxARkI2TVonTE2u6v73eSQx09tW49ME97JQicU4QVBDmNb1XcvWbicJjhcGm68dShI0AHxnwgicZZMk0Mwiahog%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <h2 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:24px 8px 8px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;text-align:left;\"><span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(1, 194, 96);font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px;\">▌出海技术挑战——Lalamove智能告警降噪</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">链接：</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link mp_article_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI0MjIxNjE0OQ==&amp;mid=2247506919&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=11f79e0cf0e6ce7cae78c54a8ababe1a&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"></a><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/_lSfD5VJV-8iRJf71z-SNA\" target=\"_blank\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/_lSfD5VJV-8iRJf71z-SNA</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">本文介绍了面对海外市场快速扩张，如何通过智能告警降噪来提升系统稳定性与用户体验。核心在于将规则化告警向动态阈值的智能算法迁移，通过时间序列预测与场景感知（节假日、天气等）来减少噪音、提升告警精度，并设计了降噪服务的可用性保障与数据处理流程，最终实现噪音下降与运营压力减轻的效果。未来还将关注模型健壮性、多时区适配，以及将生成式AI应用于告警分析。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><img data-imgfileid=\"501968442\" data-type=\"other\" width=\"839\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-w=\"839\" data-ratio=\"1.133492252681764\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b33ba812&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Fg0kpxARkI2TVonTE2u6v73eSQx09tW49fz9DzKya9pdSMoxbIfgdQjAsCmNI4QicZGXlQm2VibunS9ib2JcxL91uw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <h2 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:24px 8px 8px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;text-align:left;\"><span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(1, 194, 96);font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px;\">▌大模型原理（英文）</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">链接：</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://ngrok.com/blog/prompt-caching/\" target=\"_blank\">https://ngrok.com/blog/prompt-caching/</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1